{"TopicDetails": {"type": 0, "ccm2Id": 43840568, "cftId": 0, "identifier": "EP-COMM-SUBV-2021-EYE-Music", "title": "Music", "publicationDateLong": 1619568000000, "callIdentifier": "EP-COMM-SUBV-2021-EYE", "callTitle": "Grants in support to the European Youth Event (EYE2021) in Strasbourg", "callccm2Id": 43840582, "allowPartnerSearch": true, "workProgrammepart": {"id": 5831, "ccm_id": 43983439, "wp_part": "EP", "wp_year": "EP", "wp_title": "European Parliament", "wp_website": "https://www.europarl.europa.eu/contracts-and-grants/en/grants", "wp_document": "https://www.europarl.europa.eu/contracts-and-grants/en/grants/media-and-events"}, "frameworkProgramme": {"id": 43697167, "abbreviation": "EP", "description": "European Parliament"}, "programmeDivision": [{"id": 43697187, "abbreviation": "EP-1-1", "description": "Grants in the Area of Communication"}], "topicMGAs": [], "sme": false, "actions": [{"status": {"id": 31094503, "abbreviation": "Closed", "description": "Closed"}, "types": [{"typeOfAction": "EP-PJG EP Project Grants", "typeOfMGA": [{"id": 43694065, "abbreviation": "EP-AG", "description": "EP Action Grant Budget-Based"}]}], "plannedOpeningDate": "28 April 2021", "submissionProcedure": {"id": 31094504, "abbreviation": "single-stage", "description": "single-stage"}, "deadlineDates": ["27 May 2021"]}], "latestInfos": [], "budgetOverviewJSONItem": {"budgetTopicActionMap": {"3341971": [{"action": "EP-COMM-SUBV-2021-EYE-Sports - EP-PJG EP Project Grants", "plannedOpeningDate": "28 April 2021", "deadlineModel": "single-stage", "deadlineDates": ["27 May 2021"], "budgetYearMap": {"2021": 240000}, "budgetTopicActionMap": {}}, {"action": "EP-COMM-2021-SUBVEYE-Debates - EP-PJG EP Project Grants", "plannedOpeningDate": "28 April 2021", "deadlineModel": "single-stage", "deadlineDates": ["27 May 2021"], "budgetYearMap": {"2021": 240000}, "budgetTopicActionMap": {}}, {"action": "EP-COMM-SUBV-2021-EYE-Music - EP-PJG EP Project Grants", "plannedOpeningDate": "28 April 2021", "deadlineModel": "single-stage", "deadlineDates": ["27 May 2021"], "budgetYearMap": {"2021": 240000}, "budgetTopicActionMap": {}}]}, "budgetYearsColumns": ["2021"]}, "description": "<SPAN class=\"topicdescriptionkind\">Objective</SPAN>:<p><span><span>Design and implementation of a <strong>music programme involving artists </strong>between 16 and 30 years old, selected through a competition.</span></span></p>\n<SPAN class=\"topicdescriptionkind\">Scope</SPAN>:<p>The purpose of the music programme is to complement the activities organised under action category 1 by offering activities that create cultural understanding and acceptance through music, regardless of their language, culture or background. As for sports, music provides a universal framework for learning values, appeals to a wide audience and contributes to the development of the soft skills needed for responsible citizenship. Action category 3 aims therefore at:</p><ul level=\"0\"><li>offering a music programme that brings together EYE participants and local youth in a festive and friendly atmosphere;</li><li>supporting emerging artists from the European Union;</li><li>encouraging EYE participants and local youth to discover new emerging artists from the European Union;</li><li>raising awareness on the contribution of music to the construction of a more integrated European Union.</li> </ul>\n", "conditions": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:#404040;&#10;mso-themecolor:text1;mso-themetint:191;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Conditions</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#404040;mso-themecolor:&#10;text1;mso-themetint:191;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">1.&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Admissibility conditions: </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">described in section 5 of the call document.</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">2. Proposal page l